Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:33.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:41.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:05.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:12.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:28.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:52.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:33.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:41.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:02:05.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯著空中暢游的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:12.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉鉤上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:19.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:28.61,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這顆樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:32.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:36.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.51,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:52.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}山間回音響不絕 你說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,夜の水面に飛び交う蛍が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,流れ星みたいできれーなのん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,どこからともない雉鳩の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,モノマネしながらいく でこぼこ道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,澄み渡る星空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,いつのまにか並んで眠ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,朝日がおかえりって微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,ほら 花のこえが聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:26.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夜晚的水面上飛來飛去的螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:31.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就像是流星一般好美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:35.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知何處傳來了雉鳩的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}踏著凹凸不平的小路 邊走邊玩模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:44.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我們在繁星遍佈的澄空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:50.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知不覺就並排著睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.41,0:22:58.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}朝陽微笑著歡迎我們回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:08.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我們回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:13.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:17.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}輕輕地擁抱我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:27.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}這裡是全世界最溫暖的地方 是春天到訪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:38.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}豎起耳朵來 能聽到花兒的聲音喔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏這種日子要去菜園除草澆水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(640,220)}期末大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拿垃圾鏟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垃圾鏟是我負責的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要拿垃圾鏟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…一起拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這陣子都會像今天這樣是大晴天喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果開空調開久了就會被罵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是地獄呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.50,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 後天就開始放暑假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假我是很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我討厭熱天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天發的成績單也超討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點澆完水拔完雜草就回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做吧做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本沒試過和螢獨處呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和她聊什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.53,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H44B2FA&\pos(443,594)}與\N螢\N火\N蟲\N成\N為\N了\N好\N朋\N友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明和大家一起的時候什麼違和感都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼螢會感興趣的話題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.47,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全想不到該說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個呀 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢看過一部叫做『Pretty Cute』的動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看過呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很久以前放的那部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛與正義的美少女戰士 Pretty Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…參上噗哩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pretty Cute的招牌台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的真名是Dirty Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你們這群人咚咚地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…打扁再丟掉噗哩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最後一集的Pretty Cute呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣呢那集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的敵人竟然是主角 我嚇了一大跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 最後現出真身了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過那部我只看了最後的幾集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後放的好像是『Twinkle Sisters』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然也喜歡Pretty Cute
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最喜歡的還是那部呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前輩喜歡哪個角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的是Twinkle Black呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 雖然平時對主角很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是非常強的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有段時間還憧憬著她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『邪惡的存在 就由我來塗黑』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在主角陷入危機的時候說著這句台詞趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}帥到沒邊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢太投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法告訴她那部我只是聽說過名字而已呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不趕快改變話題的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去Twinkle星的那段也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對了螢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來穗姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是說變身為橙色的夕日一穗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是主角的前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}動畫裡面也有穗姐啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前輩最喜歡橙色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛照顧人的大姐姐這種性格很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我懂夏海前輩為什麼喜歡她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她懂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不懂但是她卻懂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 換個話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,室內鞋換成新的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙色在吐槽的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會用室內鞋敲對方的頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪的一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子都打得破破爛爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中途換了一雙新的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我看了電視…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前輩也看了昨天的重播嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太懷念那部了 也不由得看了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是拉麵節目…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和暗黑太陽神『拉·面提普托斯』大戰那段對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是橙色最好看的一幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我雖然也很喜歡橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然還是更喜歡粉色呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有粉色來著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 說是粉色 其實是紅色…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 紅色 主角那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主角是綠色呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.63,0:06:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我沒看過那部動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩 拔掉的雜草是放在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒找到好話題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就打掃完菜園了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.01,0:06:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是姐姐的話 就可以捅她腰逗她玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢的話就不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢的背上有隻壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被她發現的話就不是話題的問題了 會變成大騷動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要偷偷地…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼熱的天氣 好想跳進河裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我有點怕跳水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼熱的天氣 好想變成一隻雞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 那邊那邊 稻草人在走路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼沒關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你會怕那些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前輩害怕蜥蜴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 其實那是壁虎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全不怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蠑螈也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.42,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠑螈 聽說過但是沒見過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 很像蜥蜴和壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是在水裡生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 在水裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像科莫多巨蜥一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 因為很小所以應該叫科莫多小蜥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 那其實不是蜥蜴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢變得好積極呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次帶你去有蠑螈的池塘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池塘裡面還有蠑螈的蝌蚪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是青蛙也有蝌蚪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是兩棲動物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是蝌蚪 其實還是像小蜥蜴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}註：ウーパールーパー（uparupa），日清1985年推出的墨西哥鈍口螈吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼什麼時候去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可以嗎 好想快點去看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那回家把包放下就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壁虎壁虎壁虎壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有壁虎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把壁虎咚咚地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…打扁再丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pretty Cute最後一集…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}比大小是我贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 蓮醬 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏在草叢裡面釣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才一下鉤就釣到一大堆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洋蔥可以釣到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你們不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到垂釣那肯定是釣洋蔥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要 我也想要釣洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我胡說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在用洋蔥釣蚱蜢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用洋蔥釣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我釣了很久都沒釣到多少 正準備放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去玩點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也正在商量要去哪玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 有什麼想做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想釣洋蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了釣不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去捉蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.05,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉蟲子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠑螈的池塘剛剛才和螢去過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次很好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有帶捕蟲網呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.27,0:10:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 蓮醬 要吃這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫虎杖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣剝掉皮就能吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然在夏天可能會有點硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種草可以吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐跟我說過 路邊的野草不要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼只嚼一下也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好酸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過味道還不錯 可以有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏連蚱蜢都會釣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道得好多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有蠑螈和壁虎的區別之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 在蝙蝠前面丟小石子的話它會以為是餌然後飛下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香魚聞起來有西瓜的香味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是一大堆我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況應該怎麼形容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『天才』嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意… 忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉蟲子的話去神社怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有捕蟲網要怎麼捉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去捕蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕蟬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有捕蟲網也能捉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 去捕蟬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要夾魚背肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.63,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}日語梗：捕蟬——『せみとる』，夾魚背肉——おさかなの『せ』なかの『み』を『とる』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半自動熱水壺嗎… 半自動熱水壺嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}日語梗同上：semi auto pot——『セミ』オー『ト』ポート
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是用比較特別的方法去捉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個洞是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有蟬喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟬是在天上飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種地方怎麼會有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮醬 那個水壺裡面還有水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒喝過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會淹死的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是蟬的幼蟲喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一說 看起來和蟬蛻下來的殼一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次看到蟬的幼蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就叫做『那隻寒蟬』好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要給蟬起那種名字呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟬也捉到了 差不多該回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 幼蟲可以養嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟬的幼蟲從地裡出來之後 當天就會蛻皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,養完今天等它蛻皮之後放掉就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前輩真的知道很多東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的自由研究 我要做蟬的蛻皮觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個我也想做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩個一起觀察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還一點作業都沒做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一點點做的話 暑假結束的時候會很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我的座右銘是『有機會就玩個夠』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了蓮醬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想說我就像那隻寒蟬嗎
Comment: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,girigri梗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說的話 比較像蚱蜢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一會 蟬也飛上天空吸到甜美蜜汁了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮… 蓮華同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得大家聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開學習會太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要管作業去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才學了十分鐘呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這麼大太陽 就算去玩也熱得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到玩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天父母去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像會給我買煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有六尺玉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}六尺玉：煙火大小單位，維基表示目前號稱世界最大的煙火為四尺玉，直徑約800公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 我也可以參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想 我也想放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.29,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當然沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 在放煙火之前把今天的作業做完
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還早 學習會完了之後先暫時解散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完晚餐去螢家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我在家等你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 是個大晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要和蓮華會合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蓮醬她們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐也來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是監護人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看射上天的大煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有大煙火的話 像灑水一樣的那種也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 我們來比誰的線香煙火燒得久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不會輸喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 我們來了 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼了 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去購物的那家百貨公司的煙火都賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎什麼都沒買到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明大家都這麼期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明蓮醬 小鞠前輩 夏海前輩都很想放煙火的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 沒事的沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你說幾乎什麼都沒買到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那買到什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下這個筒狀的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 這不是很豪華的那種嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就放那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 小心點呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好… 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就點火了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 還有其它煙火嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這麼一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 呃 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中… 要開心呀… 感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降落傘煙火已經很久沒玩過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你叫我們來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.98,0:18:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.94,0:18:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說可以放煙火之後我都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天能和大家一起放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很… 開… 心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢完全沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我對不起各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 看起來比預想中更早完結了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不用哭 不用哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}螢 沒事的 沒事的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有時間 去散下步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪呢 穗姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧來吧 去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道去哪 我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走到哪呢 那邊是森林呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了找到了 就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐怎麼會知道這種地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我還以為大家都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你們也不會在晚上來這種地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢 走近點看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都光溜溜的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光溜溜？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把這個拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把葉子放進河水泡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲應該就會停在上面喝水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要加油等著它們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.43,0:21:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢和螢火蟲成為了好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.19,0:21:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒放成煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過也看到煙火了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是螢火蟲煙火呢
Comment: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跳下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄信來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影姐 你要說『叭哺叭哺』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叭哺…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.62,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H44B2FA&\pos(791,510)}一\N下\N就\N跳\N下\N去\N了
